metadata.description:
Angel_Rose 
She came from the sky...
When the battle was so overwhelming.  And there were so many dead soldiers from the both sides. Suddenly The #Golden_Ethereum called his lover  ! And the #Angel_Rose landed from the clouds and she threw her love arrow at them . Wild soldiers , they  distraught and gave up the battle !
( based on the oasis network rose )
